comments.content: Most of the car model identifications are custom designed, and I fear this one is no different. Maybe check this list of [Trajan alternatives](http://web.archive.org/web/20131022211543/http:/www.fontshop.com/fontlist/alternatives/trajan/?&sample_text=VELSATIS&sample_size=48) for a close match. [Penumbra](http://web.archive.org/) is also in the ballpark.
